			<hr class='short'>
			<div class='section-text'>Many patients come to us because they are experiencing symptoms of depression, anxiety, trauma, and attention deficit disorders. Others search for treatment when being challenged with psychoses, substance abuse, family discord, or domestic violence. Regardless of what you are experiencing, understand that it is our upmost duty to help you throughout the entire process.
