			    <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
			      <h5 class="mb-0">
			        <button class="btn btn-link" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#when" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
			        	When Is It Time to Seek Treatment?
			        </button>
			      </h5>
			    </div>

			    <div id="when" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
			      <div class="card-body section-text">
			      	Early warning signs that indicate you may need to seek help:
			      	<ul>
						<li>Feeling sad, negative, depressed</li>
						<li>Having low self-esteem</li>
						<li>Experiencing unexplained aches and pains</li> 
						<li>Having zero to no energy </li>
						<li>Experiencing loss in memory, loss of interest in activities</li> 
						<li>Suffering from anxiety or panic attacks</li>
						<li>Thinking of harming yourself for others</li>
						<li>Experiencing uncontrollable stress, fears and obsessions</li>
						<li>Problems with drug, alcohol addictions, or eating disorders</li>
						<li>Facing conflict with family members or significant others</li>
					</ul>
			      </div>
			    </div>
			  </div>
			  <div class="card">
			    <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
			      <h5 class="mb-0">
			        <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#begin" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
			          Before Beginning Therapy
			        </button>
			      </h5>
			    </div>
			    <div id="begin" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
			      <div class="card-body section-text">
			        Ask yourself these questions:
			        <ul>
			        	<li>Why do I need to begin therapy sessions?</li>
						<li>Why now?</li>
						<li>Am I ready to commit now?</li>
						<li>Do I have any goals for therapy?</li>
						<li>What will be different in my life when I reach my goals?</li>
						<li>How important is it that I achieve these goals?</li>
						<li>Am I ready for change?</li>
						<li>What am I willing to let go of to allow myself to move forward in my life? </li>
					</ul>
			      </div>
